Sweden
One of our three core global R&D centres is located in Sweden, Gothenburg. Here, our research focuses on Respiratory, Inflammation, and Autoimmunity Diseases (RIA), Cardiovascular and Metabolic Diseases (CVMD).  Sweden is also home to our largest production and supply site, which is located in Södertälje, near Stockholm. 
