UK
AstraZeneca is a major contributor to UK science and innovation investment, economic prosperity and to patient health. We have several sites across the country, including major research and production sites at Alderley Park and Luton. And of course, the UK is also home to our new Global R&D Centre and Corporate Headquarters in Cambridge. We see the UK as being at the heart of AstraZeneca’s efforts to develop new medicines.
